Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:33.88,top,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:36.36,top,MASHA,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Alya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.74,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.13,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm home, Masha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:46.00,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Come on! I told you to \Ncall me Onee-chan in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.00,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,No, not after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.24,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Boo, you meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:56.70,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,You seem kinda down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:58.12,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.01,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,No? Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:04.52,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Lies. You can't deceive my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:07.46,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Tell me, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:10.14,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,It's really not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:14.90,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I just met Kuze-kun \Nand his childhood friend. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:16.78,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Ah, him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:17.63,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:23.37,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,You just get really \Nworked up when it comes to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.83,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:33.79,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Finally, a boy who can move \Nyour heart has showed up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.80,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:39.30,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,You like this Kuze-kun, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:42.93,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I don't know what gave you that silly idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:45.44,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,but he and I aren't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.64,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,We are, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:51.06,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Right, we are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:54.86,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah? How did you become friends, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:58.97,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,I know you hate indifferent slackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.26,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Well, yeah...
