Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.36,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:31.59,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,I was wrong to expect anything from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:37.70,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,I feel like nobody is ever as driven as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.11,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.30,flashback italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,then I'll just do everything all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:03.30,flashback,GIRL3,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:07.13,flashback,GIRL3,0,0,0,,Is it true you passed \Nthat crazy difficult transfer exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.33,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I guess I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:11.66,flashback,BOY2,0,0,0,,Your Japanese is great, Kujo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.57,flashback,BOY2,0,0,0,,Have you lived in Japan before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.64,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yes, I lived here until five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.65,flashback,GIRL3,0,0,0,,Talk to you later, Kujo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:26.41,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,He slept through that racket?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:30.00,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Hey, the warning bell's ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:36.79,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, you the transfer student who did \Nthat speech at the opening ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:38.58,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yes, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:43.04,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm Alisa Mikhailovna Kujo. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:46.17,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hi. I'm Kuze Masachika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.48,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:50.78,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:53.33,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Heya, Hikaru. Didn't know \Nyou were in this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:54.67,flashback,HIKARU,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.67,flashback,HIKARU,0,0,0,,Takeshi's here too, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.23,flashback,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So he is.
